text:
lets imagine i'm restructuring the code behind one of our main customer facing pages: the calc page. it's a nextjs app and essentially displays a bunch of package options to the customer so that they can explore the price and learn about different components.

we fetch all the data we need from the backend from an Interest endpoint. Interest is the main object holding all information we need, including packages etc.

